ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR GAMELOG:

This project encourages collaborative development. If you use this code:

1. CONTRIBUTE BACK: We strongly encourage contributing improvements back to the original GameLog project
2. OPEN SOURCE REQUIREMENT: Any derivative work must also be open source under GPL v3
3. NO PROPRIETARY FORKS: You cannot create closed-source commercial versions
4. ATTRIBUTION: You must credit the original GameLog project and contributors

For the full GPL v3 license text, visit: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html

---

CONTRIBUTING TO GAMELOG:

We welcome contributions! Here's how to get involved:

• Fork the repository on GitHub
• Create a feature branch for your changes
• Submit a pull request with a clear description
• Follow our coding standards and guidelines
• Join our community discussions

By contributing to GameLog, you help build a better gaming platform for everyone while ensuring the project remains free and open source.